OL,3,CLincolnshire worst in country for
OL,4,Cdrownings last year
OL,6,FLincolnshire has recorded the highest
OL,7,Fnumber of accidental drowning deaths
OL,8,Fin England last year as national
OL,9,Ffigures highlight the dangers of
OL,10,Finland waterways.
OL,12,FEight accidental drowning deaths were
OL,13,Frecorded in Lincolnshire in 2025.
OL,15,FFigures published today by the
OL,16,FNational Water Safety Forum (NWSF)
OL,17,Fshow that inland waterways accounted
OL,18,Ffor the majority of accidental
OL,19,Fdrowning deaths across the UK for the
OL,20,Fseventh consecutive year in 2025.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
