OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780233072
OL,3,CLincolnshire worst in country for
OL,4,Cdrownings last year
OL,6,FNationally, 202 people accidentally
OL,7,Flost their lives in water-related
OL,8,Fincidents last year, with 57% of
OL,9,Ffatalities occurring inland in rivers,
OL,10,Flakes, reservoirs, canals, quarry
OL,11,Flakes and other open water locations.
OL,13,FThe warning comes as seven children
OL,14,Fand two adults die in open water
OL,15,Fincidents over Bank Holiday amid
OL,16,Frecord-breaking temperatures across
OL,17,Fthe UK.
OL,19,FThe body of 15-year-old Declan Sawyer,
OL,20,Fwas found in a Lincoln lake on Sunday,
OL,21,F24 May, around 10.25pm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780233072
OL,3,CLincolnshire worst in country for
OL,4,Cdrownings last year
OL,6,FDeclan's father Carl described him as
OL,7,F"a funny and outgoing young man who
OL,8,Floved fishing and football," as he
OL,9,Fcalled on families to take care of
OL,10,Ftheir children when near water.
OL,12,F"He had a very cheeky smile and the
OL,13,Fpersonality to match. He was very much
OL,14,Floved by his friends and family, and
OL,15,Fwill be missed dearly by many," Carl
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"Please can all parents, friends and
OL,19,Ffamily make their children aware of
OL,20,Fthe dangers surrounding water."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780233072
OL,3,CLincolnshire worst in country for
OL,4,Cdrownings last year
OL,6,FThese warnings have been reiterated by
OL,7,Fanother father who's 16-year-old son,
OL,8,FSam Haycock, died at a reservoir in
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire almost five years ago.
OL,11,FSince then he has been tirelessly
OL,12,Fcampaigning for better water safety
OL,13,Fand wants parents to "get the message
OL,14,Facross to them about the dangers
OL,15,Fbecause that water doesn't
OL,16,Fdiscriminate".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780233072
OL,3,CLincolnshire worst in country for
OL,4,Cdrownings last year
OL,6,FFollowing Declan's death, a new
OL,7,Fpetition has been started in Lincoln
OL,8,Fto try and improve water safety around
OL,9,Fthe city and there are calls to create
OL,10,Fa new dedicated swimming facility for
OL,11,Ffamilies to enjoy.
OL,13,FHowever, the message coming from
OL,14,Fauthorities about existing inland
OL,15,Fwaterways is to stay out of the water
OL,16,Faltogether.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
