CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1780233072
OL,3,CLincolnshire worst in country for
OL,4,Cdrownings last year
OL,6,FMark Baxter, Chief Fire Officer at
OL,7,FLincolnshire Fire and Rescue said: "It
OL,8,Fmay look really inviting on a warm
OL,9,Fday, but the water temperature is
OL,10,Fstill really cold.
OL,12,F"If you go into the water in that
OL,13,Ftemperature, the cold water shock will
OL,14,Fabsolutely stop your ability to swim."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
