OL,3,CLincolnshire worst in country for
OL,4,Cdrownings last year
OL,6,FIf someone gets into difficulty in the
OL,7,Fwater, the public is being encouraged
OL,8,Fto follow the NWSF's "Phone Float
OL,9,FThrow" advice: Phone 999 immediately,
OL,10,Fencourage the person to float on their
OL,11,Fback and throw rescue equipment if
OL,12,Favailable.
